title: Looking for team mates for ranked 5
body:
I am looking for dedicated league of legend players who are willing to practise and do ranked 5 games competitively. Anyone can apply from lvl 30, you dont have to be a great rank to join the team but you have to be willing to learn new game styles and be able to adapt to any situation. For communication we will be using skype or curse. if interested pls comment your ingame name below

I am looking for the following roles ( will take subs too):
